/* =====================================================
    Module;
     .ui-multilineEllipsis

    Variations;
     -three
     -four

    Notes;
     - Truncate String ... â€¦
     - The cacluation to display more lines is (line-height*lines*1em)

    Reading Material: 
     - http://html5hub.com/ellipse-my-text/
